{"tid":2052334,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人隻貓絕完育呼吸會快咗？","createTime":"2020-06-05T12:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T19:14:45.000Z","uid":22885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb53e2589b406aad0869c35501877c385c7edbf","tid":2052334,"uid":22885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:35:27.000Z","msg":"今日帶隻貓去絕育 加埋驗血<br />\n<br />\n結果就所有野都好正常 <br />\n<br />\n帶佢返屋企之後一陣 佢就呼吸變快變急 仲不時伸條脷出嚟抖氣<br />\n<br />\n我即刻再打比醫生 佢就話可能因為熱同緊張 所以有機會會咁 叫我留意多一陣先<br />\n<br />\n到而家帶咗返嚟大約4個鐘 佢啲呼吸都係快  都係周不時伸條脷出嚟 但係頻率少咗<br />\n<br />\n我上網爬文就話 痛 都會令到佢呼吸快 <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似情況？<br />\n<br />\n利申：打算聽日都係帶佢去睇睇醫生"},{"pid":"8ca7fc303d0df8d398544778f4c7d8e3f2eb6756","tid":2052334,"uid":210831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"我隻貓早排絕完育 返到屋企果陣都係咁<br />\n應該係因為熱所以係咁張開口唞氣 同埋d麻醉藥未散 佢睇落會瞳孔放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢第2日就冇乜野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad0cc8e255d2a72e2d7f38eef18d92729478be4","tid":2052334,"uid":22885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ca7fc303d0df8d398544778f4c7d8e3f2eb6756","tid":2052334,"uid":210831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"我隻貓早排絕完育 返到屋企果陣都係咁<br />\n應該係因為熱所以係咁張開口唞氣 同埋d麻醉藥未散 佢睇落會瞳孔放大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢第2日就冇乜野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"想問下你隻貓第一日呼吸都係好快？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4337e626994ad602167c8d06a2acc807b6b47a23","tid":2052334,"uid":210831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad0cc8e255d2a72e2d7f38eef18d92729478be4","tid":2052334,"uid":22885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ca7fc303d0df8d398544778f4c7d8e3f2eb6756","tid":2052334,"uid":210831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTim